{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":6042,"text":"This is a kindergarten\nwe designed in 2007."},{"time":10111,"text":"We made this kindergarten \nto be a circle."},{"time":14036,"text":"It's a kind of endless circulation\non top of the roof."},{"time":17179,"text":"If you are a parent,"},{"time":19699,"text":"you know that kids love\nto keep making circles."},{"time":24793,"text":"This is how the rooftop looks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":27600,"text":"And why did we design this?"},{"time":29858,"text":"The principal of this kindergarten said,"},{"time":32675,"text":"\"No, I don't want a handrail.\""},{"time":35254,"text":"I said, \"It's impossible.\""},{"time":37483,"text":"But he insisted: \"How about having a net\nsticking out from the edge of the roof?"},{"time":43777,"text":"So that it can catch\nthe children falling off?\""},{"time":45986,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":47433,"text":"I said, \"It's impossible.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":49970,"text":"And of course,\nthe government official said,"},{"time":52889,"text":"\"Of course you have to have a handrail.\""},{"time":58324,"text":"But we could keep \nthat idea around the trees."},{"time":61843,"text":"There are three trees popping through."},{"time":65120,"text":"And we were allowed to call \nthis rope as a handrail."},{"time":70745,"text":"But of course, rope has nothing\nto do with them."},{"time":74017,"text":"They fall into the net."},{"time":77304,"text":"And you get more,"},{"time":80355,"text":"and more,"},{"time":83292,"text":"more."},{"time":84502,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":85653,"text":"Sometimes 40 children \nare around a tree."},{"time":91733,"text":"The boy on the branch,"},{"time":92981,"text":"he loves the tree\nso he is eating the tree."},{"time":95464,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":98984,"text":"And at the time of an event,"},{"time":100785,"text":"they sit on the edge."},{"time":104191,"text":"It looks so nice from underneath."},{"time":106563,"text":"Monkeys in the zoo."},{"time":108652,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":112552,"text":"Feeding time."},{"time":114318,"text":"(Laughter) \n(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":120784,"text":"And we made the roof as low as possible,"},{"time":123313,"text":"because we wanted to see\nchildren on top of the roof,"},{"time":127757,"text":"not only underneath the roof."},{"time":130438,"text":"And if the roof is too high,\nyou see only the ceiling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":135699,"text":"And the leg washing place --\nthere are many kinds of water taps."},{"time":140656,"text":"You see with the flexible tubes,"},{"time":142434,"text":"you want to spray water\nto your friends,"},{"time":145329,"text":"and the shower,"},{"time":147044,"text":"and the one in front is quite normal."},{"time":149541,"text":"But if you look at this,"},{"time":151087,"text":"the boy is not washing his boots,"},{"time":152917,"text":"he's putting water into his boots."},{"time":154591,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":161423,"text":"This kindergarten is completely\nopen, most of the year."},{"time":167699,"text":"And there is no boundary\nbetween inside and outside."},{"time":171339,"text":"So it means basically\nthis architecture is a roof."},{"time":175978,"text":"And also there is no boundary\nbetween classrooms."},{"time":179267,"text":"So there is no acoustic barrier at all."},{"time":183590,"text":"When you put many children in a quiet box,"},{"time":189415,"text":"some of them get really nervous."},{"time":192733,"text":"But in this kindergarten,"},{"time":194985,"text":"there is no reason they get nervous."},{"time":198415,"text":"Because there is no boundary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":201225,"text":"And the principal says"},{"time":203422,"text":"if the boy in the corner\ndoesn't want to stay in the room,"},{"time":207425,"text":"we let him go."},{"time":209120,"text":"He will come back eventually,\nbecause it's a circle, it comes back."},{"time":212279,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":216561,"text":"But the point is,\nin that kind of occasion,"},{"time":219556,"text":"usually children try to hide somewhere."},{"time":222407,"text":"But here, just they leave and come back."},{"time":226986,"text":"It's a natural process."}]},{"cues":[{"time":228836,"text":"And secondly, we consider\nnoise very important."},{"time":235711,"text":"You know that children\nsleep better in noise."},{"time":242142,"text":"They don't sleep in a quiet space."},{"time":245986,"text":"And in this kindergarten,"},{"time":248236,"text":"these children show\namazing concentration in class."},{"time":255193,"text":"And you know, our kind grew up\nin the jungle with noise."},{"time":261660,"text":"They need noise."},{"time":263663,"text":"And you know, you can talk\nto your friends in a noisy bar."},{"time":267967,"text":"You are not supposed to be in silence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271928,"text":"And you know, these days"},{"time":274095,"text":"we are trying to make\neverything under control."},{"time":280219,"text":"You know, it's completely open."},{"time":282021,"text":"And you should know that"},{"time":285033,"text":"we can go skiing in -20 degrees in winter."},{"time":290818,"text":"In summer you go swimming."},{"time":293922,"text":"The sand is 50 degrees."},{"time":296636,"text":"And also, you should know\nthat you are waterproof."},{"time":300029,"text":"You never melt in rain."},{"time":303181,"text":"So, children are supposed to be outside."},{"time":307050,"text":"So that is how we should treat them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":310251,"text":"This is how they divide classrooms."},{"time":312923,"text":"They are supposed to help teachers."},{"time":315426,"text":"They don't."},{"time":317731,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":323226,"text":"I didn't put him in."},{"time":327522,"text":"A classroom."},{"time":330196,"text":"And a washbasin."},{"time":332655,"text":"They talk to each other around the well."},{"time":337082,"text":"And there are always \nsome trees in the classroom."},{"time":343969,"text":"A monkey trying to fish\nanother monkey from above."},{"time":347377,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":349225,"text":"Monkeys."},{"time":350829,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":352283,"text":"And each classroom has\nat least one skylight."},{"time":357468,"text":"And this is where Santa Claus\ncomes down at the time of Christmas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":367255,"text":"This is the annex building,"},{"time":369682,"text":"right next to that\noval-shaped kindergarten."},{"time":374151,"text":"The building is only\nfive meters tall with seven floors."},{"time":379810,"text":"And of course,\nthe ceiling height is very low."},{"time":381971,"text":"So you have to consider safety."},{"time":386036,"text":"So, we put our children,\na daughter and a son."},{"time":391707,"text":"They tried to go in."},{"time":395731,"text":"He hit his head."},{"time":399343,"text":"He's okay. His skull is quite strong."},{"time":403312,"text":"He is resilient. It's my son."},{"time":406400,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":409038,"text":"And he is trying to see\nif it is safe to jump off."},{"time":413038,"text":"And then we put other children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420835,"text":"The traffic jam is awful\nin Tokyo, as you know."},{"time":423376,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":424528,"text":"The driver in front,\nshe needs to learn how to drive."},{"time":429379,"text":"Now these days,"},{"time":431910,"text":"kids need a small dosage of danger."},{"time":438970,"text":"And in this kind of occasion,"},{"time":441375,"text":"they learn to help each other."},{"time":445300,"text":"This is society. This is the kind of\nopportunity we are losing these days."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456065,"text":"Now, this drawing is showing\nthe movement of a boy"},{"time":462976,"text":"between 9:10 and 9:30."},{"time":469300,"text":"And the circumference\nof this building is 183 meters."},{"time":475501,"text":"So it's not exactly small at all."},{"time":479353,"text":"And this boy did 6,000 meters\nin the morning."},{"time":483959,"text":"But the surprise is yet to come."},{"time":487551,"text":"The children in this kindergarten\ndo 4,000 meters on average."},{"time":495455,"text":"And these children have\nthe highest athletic abilities"},{"time":502435,"text":"among many kindergartens."},{"time":511390,"text":"The principal says,"},{"time":513016,"text":"\"I don't train them.\nWe leave them on top of the roof."},{"time":519353,"text":"Just like sheep.\""},{"time":520972,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":522401,"text":"They keep running."},{"time":524230,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":526779,"text":"My point is don't control them,"},{"time":531838,"text":"don't protect them too much,"},{"time":535060,"text":"and they need to tumble sometimes."},{"time":538687,"text":"They need to get some injury."},{"time":542473,"text":"And that makes them learn"},{"time":545892,"text":"how to live in this world."},{"time":551848,"text":"I think architecture is capable\nof changing this world,"},{"time":559057,"text":"and people's lives."},{"time":561909,"text":"And this is one of the attempts\nto change the lives of children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568481,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570158,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}